Further, TRPL spectroscopy was conducted to probe the exciton and biexciton dynamics. Quantitatively under the condition of thermal equilibrium, the time evolution of the exciton and biexciton can be modeled with the transition function59nbx~nbx0e-2t∕τex\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
